properties.text: The digit on each tile represents the number of mines in the surrounding 8 tiles.
An empty tile means that every tile around it are safe.
Left-click on a hidden tile to uncover it.
Right-click on a tile to mark to mark a mine.
Left-click on an open tile to open all surrounding tiles if the number of flags is equal to the number on that tile.
Left-click on an open tile to mark all surrounding tiles if the number of hidden tiles is equal to the number on that tile.
